text:
This is Angela chen
reporting live from the site
of a massive battle

between the justice league
and a group of what can
only be described

as super-villains
calling themselves
the legion of doom.

Reports state that earlier,
the legion launched
a surprise attack

on the league at the unveiling
of their new headquarters,

dubbed by many
on social media as
"the hall of justice."

Is this any way to treat
your guests, superman?

Seeing as how you
crashed the party,
I'd consider us even.

Did mama kick you
out of the basement?

Well at hand, father.
As predicted, they respond
like contemptible sheep.

This doesn't have
to end in violence.

I'm simply
an innocent industrialist
caught in the middle.

But I enjoy
a good game.

Too bad shazam and lantern
had to miss the fun.

Come on, wizard,
don't make me hit you again.

The hour of his rising
is at hand.

Hmm. What the hell
did he hit me with?

Robin, get all civilians
inside, do you read me?

I have a more efficient way
to keep them safe, father.

Robin?
 Robin, I gave you a task.

Yes, as a human cattle prod.
I'm being under-utilized.

Between the missile
and fuel cell detonations,

I'd estimate at least
a three kiloton hit.

The lasso compels you
to obey my command!

I thought that would knock
the fight out of him.
What? We got him, didn't we?

What we have is an empty shell
with no answers.

If you had followed orders
and done what you're told,
we'd know more.

Come on,
cut him some slack.
At least, he was trying to...

You buried me
in a worthless position
to keep me out of the way.

And I solved
the entire problem.

All I see is a lot
of ineffectual grandstanding.

Which is why I prefer
to work alone.

And my dad
thinks I'm difficult.

Have you ever considered
boarding school?

You're lucky to be allowed
within 10 feet
of a steering wheel.

Enduring a bunch
of school children?

Hopefully, you'll learn
to be a part of a team.

And they're not children.
They're teenagers.

Don't tell me
Damian Wayne is afraid
of a little socializing.
Then what am I to you?

You were having
a nightmare last night.

I was just wondering
if everything's...

Look, I appreciate
your concern, I guess.
But they're dreams.

Forgot to put on my uniform.
Okay? So I sleep in the nude.
So what?

I'm the entire animal kingdom
crammed into a single
magnificent specimen.
What did that thing just say?
It was just laughing at you.

Yow! Keep that thing
on a leash, man!
I told you, don't annoy it.
That scarab is not a pet.

It may be fused
to Jaime's spine,

but it's not exactly
under his control.
It's like you and your pants.

To help each other
control our gifts.

Help one another
become our best selves.

Where else are we gonna go?
I mean, we're a bunch
of freaks, right?

Come on, Jaime,
we're all family.
Like the three amigos.

-Would you like to...
-I think I can manage.

Yeah, I was thinking a movie
might be nice.
Just you and me.

By the way, I bought
some new glasses.

I'm sure I'll be able
to pick you out

If this is a prank,
you're screwing
with the wrong guy.

He hasn't stopped
for an hour and a half.

Damian, it's time
to let others have their turn.

Hmph, I heard your tech
was fast.
I wanted to see how fast.

Don't mess with us,
little man.

I can see we are getting off
on the wrong foot.
Damian, this is a team effort.

We need to be willing
to accommodate others.

Nightwing said
you were a Princess.

And like it or not,
i am the leader
of this group.

As I see it, you're an alien
with nowhere else to go.

Thank you for chiming in,
witch girl.

We are only here
to help you realize
your potential.

When do you think
you'll realize yours?

Dude, you need
to show some respect.

Who's fighting me,
you or the bug?

That's the difference
between you and me.

This is going to be
an awkward call to Batman.

By the powers of azarath,
i beseech you.

We need to get her
back to her room.

Raven healed you.
We have to tend to her.

I knew you'd be here
working all night.

Where does all that food go
if you don't have a stomach?

I've been combing
through footage from
every camera on the grid.

Dark spots.
They're hard to make out.

No, the sun direction
is wrong.

And look here,
it's disconnected
from the surface.

It's wandering,
like it's looking
for something.

There's where weather wizard
ran into it.

You don't think
it was after him.

Don't get me wrong,
i love catching up
on popular culture

but the harsh language
was entirely unnecessary,

and the female lead seemed
to only be present in order
to be rescued

But all in all,
i found myself
reasonably diverted.

I've got a lot on my mind
right now.

You can always share
your burdens with me, Clark.

You could put out an eye
with that thing.

Didn't your mother tell you
never to play with knives?

Mother spirit
of the nether realm,

And give me strength
to face the dark force
i fear is coming.

I suppose I should thank you
for healing me.

It was strange
having you in my head.

I felt you prying
into my entire life.

I'm an empath, and if it
makes you feel any better,

I didn't see it
as much as felt it.

And I've been trying
to shake it off ever since.

Then you know
I'm not meant to be here
at this stupid school.

I was groomed
for a higher calling.

I know all about
your grandfather.
I felt him. He was a demon.

And believe me,
i know my demons.

We were going to make
the world stronger, better.

We were going
to rule it together.

I know all about
that game, too.

Now, I don't mean to be rude,
but would you mind getting
the hell away from me?

You know, when you were
in my head, I could see things
about you, too.
It was real, I could tell.

It's none of your business.
Who are you to judge my life?

You have other things
to fix here.
Just stay away from me, okay?

Can you please do that
anywhere else?

Perhaps it was a mistake
to challenge you this morning
without knowing

the full capacity
of your alien attachment.

I promise you,
it won't happen again.
Did he just say he's sorry?

We had quite a tumble
last year.

Still, I sensed you,
being a good guy and all,
playing nice.
You won't have to this time.

I've gotten
a lot, lot, stronger.

He's barely alive, Clark,
what's wrong with you?

Guess he doesn't
tell you everything.
You have your part to play.

With any luck,
military satellites
are tracking him now.

Pull the moon
from the sky?

He hasn't said anything
about doing something
like that, has he?

We're both targets
and for all we know,
so is the rest of the league.

Get back to that island
of yours

and lock yourself
in the darkest, deepest tomb
you can find.
You can't expect me to hide.
What are you doing in my room?

You never trespass
another person's space.

You have nothing on her.
No background, no history.

You're the leader
of this group.

You should know everything
about her.

She grew up
in a hostile realm,
not unlike my own planet.
And she escaped, like I did.

We didn't know anything
about raven
when we took her in
except that she needed a home.

I was taught that knowledge
was power and you knew
nothing about her.

How much do you have to know
when people are in need?

Garfield was 11
when his genetics kicked in
and gave him green skin

We still don't know
the purpose of Jaime's
alien armor
We just knew they needed help.

You have to have
a little faith sometimes.

Faith is belief
based on an absence of data.

You have no idea
how frustrating it is.
He reminds me of my sister.

I told you he was tough.
 Never had a childhood.

Doesn't know how to act
 with kids or anyone else
 for that matter.

Well, you can't expect him
 to be great at bonding.

Spent most of his life
 training to kill.

Then moves in
 with the big bad bat,

You know, kori,
 you and I could just...

That's it,
that's what we need.

Oh, you're so smart.
Thanks, dick.

I wondered
when you'd get back.

Flash is checking the area,
he just disappeared.
Where the hell is he going?

You have my feed
from the Batmobile?

The entity was strong enough
to possess a Kryptonian.

It can't stay in the host
if the host is damaged.

If I'd poisoned superman
with a bigger dose,
i might have saved him.

Scour the net,
narrow your search results
to superman sightings

Aah! Dude, did you have
to bring the sword?

Preparedness is a prerequisite
for victory.

The gear stays
in the car, Damian.

Tonight we are to enjoy
some mandatory fun.

This is an opportunity for us
to become more familiar
with each other.

How much more
familiar can we get?

We've already seen
Garfield lick himself.

Boy, were you
up in those mountains
a long time.

It was a joke,
I'm not criticizing.
I knew it was a joke.

And if you knew me,
you wouldn't waste
your time trying.

I guess neither of
our lives are very funny.

But I'll tell you something
about yourself that
not even you know.

but in your heart,
you are a kind
and generous soul.

Oh, looks like we found
something the bug can't do.

Free popcorn to anyone
who can slay the beast.

On the hill,
 beyond the tent.
It can't be him, it's a trick.

Never leave unfinished
 what you start.

If you were really here,
I'd smell your stink.

All you can send
are these losers.

It's our destiny
 to be together,
 raven, always.
I will fight you every step.

-You're an abomination.
 -Watch your talk,
 ungrateful girl.

It is beneath my contempt
 and I will not have it.

You will be a part of
 this, child.

You will know
 the glory of trigon.

Mother of azarath,
give me strength.

You cannot last.
You're temporal agents.

You were
very good too, Garfield.

They're demonic emissaries.
My father sent them.

Yes, but you can't stop them
like that.

Whoo, yeah, we kicked
demon boot-ay.

Robin said I didn't know
enough about you.

You told me
you didn't have a father.

What I said is that
he's gone.
That's not the same as dead.

So, why is he
trying to kill you?
He's not trying to kill me.

Safe to say we're not in
Kansas anymore.

It's no star field
i recognize.

Somewhere my father
can't see us.
I guess it starts with my mom.

She was young, rebellious
 and gullible.

Of course she wound up
 in a cult.

they decided to do
 the classic bride of
 Satan rite.

And guess who got
 to be the lucky bride?

I doubt anyone
 expected it to work,

but the ancient ceremony
 turned out to be
 the real thing.

with her great powers
 of judgment,

didn't hesitate to hook up
 with the guy who emerged
 from the smoke.

So, your mom
did it with Satan?

His name is trigon,
but basically, yes.

Mom fled the cult
and was on the run
with nowhere to go,

when she gets saved by
these people from
another dimension.

A realm of beauty,
 peace and tranquility

where, needless to say,
 I did not fit in.

And I must have inherited
 my mom's terrible judgment

because I thought if
 I found out more about
 the monster who made me,

I'd be able to
 make sense of myself.

He took me to his
hellish universe.

I could hardly bear
the horrors I saw there.

He wanted earth.
He's a conqueror of worlds.

But he needs a
powerful conduit
to open earth to his control.

But my magic was stronger
than he realized.

Before he could use me,
 I was able to trap him
 inside a crystal.

Perhaps if I had
 stayed there,

Why didn't you go back
to azarath?

I've got to keep moving
to keep trigon off my path.

He's going to try to use you
but don't worry,

I put a protective spell
on you, just in case.

And I thought I had
a bad burrito.

Guess I should've gotten
your permission or whatever.

But I couldn't stand for him
to corrupt you.

You're the only friends
I've ever really had.

Leave now and you'll
always be running.

You have no idea
what he's like, Damian.

You've never met
a monster like trigon.

Now you'll be four times
as lucky.

If we can't save
one of our own,

I'm not wishing you
dead anymore.

Robin's right,
we are your best hope.

Her father is
an inter-dimensional demon.
He was after her.

If she's part of this,
we need to know.

I'm sorry, raven.
We've had two magic attacks
and superman is still missing.

He knows they're here,
he wants them here.

If they stay,
everything will be lost.

This is our job, father,
you have to leave.

Maybe we should all
take a breath.

The Kryptonian has unearthed
the infernal shrine, raven.

An ancient shrine
built by satanists.

You are the shrine's
final piece.

I stop my hand for an instant
and this one dies, too.

I'll go. As the daughter of
your lord trigon,

I order you to release
these feeble humans.

There had better be
 no trickery this time, girl,

if you want any mercy
 shown your friends.

Look, I'm begging you,
leave this world alone.
We were meant to be together.

-Did that sound
demonic to anyone else?
-A little.
The things it made me see.
Cyborg, how do we save raven?
Oh, no. How bad is he?

risked death to give us
a fighting chance at life.

Which is more than I can say
for the rest of the league.

Damian, this isn't
the time to squabble.
We have to get raven back.

We don't even know
where she is.

She's in the middle east,
60 miles north
of kahndaq city.

-How do you...
-I put a tracer on her.

Same time I put one
on each of you.

Cyborg, you have the ability
to manifest boom tubes,
do you not?
Yeah, I can boom us there.

But you guys barely held
your own against flash
and wonder woman,

and that's without superman
being on deck.

Yeah, right, like you got
a way to take out superman.
Oh, my god, I think he does.

I've got flash,
the rest of you
get raven off that thing.

Barry, if you can hear me
in there,

How long will it take you
to heal?

Ah, oh, my god,
an hour?

Your power is no match for
that of trigon, Kryptonian.

She doesn't belong
to you, devil.
Let me go, you alien filth.

You can get off my back now,
boy bony-ass.

-There's only one way.
-You're going to put him back
in the crystal.

In the unlikely event
that I can make it there.
Oh, I don't feel so good.

The crystal can only
be touched by me.

He may have escaped it,
but he can't destroy it.

I just hope he left a trail
of breadcrumbs.

Can't you just
transport us inside?

Maybe this
will slow you down.

-If we cannot stop
this creature...
-I know.
It's a trick. I saw you die.

No trick. It's me.
I assure you.

How do you think I attained
my power?

Where do you think
the Lazarus pits came from?

and he can make things
whole again for a price.

He can give us the world
we wanted.
You and I. A perfect world.

She's the only one
who stands in the way.
Take care of this for me.

Before my pact
with trigon expires.

I... I would do anything
to bring you back,

Are you afraid to do
the one act that will
restore me to life?

You think your allies
 can stop me
 now that I'm here?

The justice league,
 defenders of this realm,
 less than insects to me.

I will strip bare the flesh
 from their bones.

And your pathetic friends,
 I will make them
 suffer endlessly,
and you will have to watch.

Soon, your souls will belong
 to trigon,

Your friends
have made you soft.

You could have been immortal,
like me.

You're too weak
 to stop me, raven.

No, my only weakness
 was loving you,
hoping I'd be loved in return.

But all you were capable
 of giving is pain,

friends I would give
 my life for,
and the strength to do this.

Grant me the strength
of mighty azarath

to contain the demon trigon
within this sacred shard,
now and forever.

Trigon will spend
every single minute
trying to get out of here,

so he needs to be watched
every single minute.

It was nice to have
a big gun around.

Yeah, you ought to dump
those stuck-up jerks
and sign up with us.

It was nice not to be
the kid for once,

but when you've been
in the majors...

When you have to go there,
they have to take you in.

Robert frost.
You are full of surprises,
Damian.

I've sifted through
 all the data

and found no signs
 of the corruptors
 for the 10 days

In other words,
 great work, titans.

Your determination
 and teamwork saved the world,

and us. You should be
 very proud of them, kori.

He always said
we should be together.

That's gotta be torture
for him.

Well, you can take the girl
out of hell...

You're too weak
 to keep me in here,
 you filthy witch!

I'll get out!
 I'll kill everyone you love.
